0.1.4.readme:
# Glowcal Hubot Scripts

Utility scripts to help operate the Glowcal domain.

## Deployment

Publish as npm package called `hubot-gc`.

## Commands

### Registration Keys

    hubot glowcal regkey

Returns a new registration key
